caption: It would be a dream come true to meet Jack and Jack! I live around the Pittsburgh area so not that many artists I enjoy come to Pittsburgh. But Jack and Jack have helped me through so much and I have always supported them since day 1. I'm bullied and talked about a lot in school and I have many insecurities about myself and I try to not let many people into my life if I don't trust them. But I would always feel so bad about myself and I would just go through some of Johnson's and Gilinsky's tweets and they would help put a smile on my face and cheer me up. So anyone that can do that for me really means a lot. I always run away from myself and I don't really accept who I really am and I'm finally learning how to accept myself because of Jack and Jack. So if I won these tickets for this contest it would mean a lot because I would love to personally thank them for everything that they've done for me and for other people as well. So anyone that can save a person's life really deserves it. So if I won this contest I would love to meet them and thank them for all of the positive messages that helped me through my tough times these past years. ? #contest
